## Working conventions (from CLAUDE.md + prior feedback)

- **Surgical changes.** Touch only what the task needs. Don't refactor adjacent code,
  reformat, or delete pre-existing dead code (mention it instead). Match existing style.
- **Simplicity first.** Minimum code; no speculative abstractions or config.
